    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed. The interior is spotless and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
