    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for your absolute dream ride? This car is a total gem and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it was brand new. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. You really have to see it to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this beauty go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
