    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46), a superlative example of the marque's engineering peak. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to achieve a linear 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The exterior maintains its factory depth with no swirl marks, while the interior leather retains its original matte finish. Mechanically synchronized and free of fluid weeping, this M3 represents a turn-key opportunity for the purist collector.",
